Saurin karuwa a yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan ci gaba a ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, wanda ke tabbatar da cewa ko da yake a matakai daban-daban, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da Italiya ta fuskanta, ƙasashe, asibitoci da sassan kula da marasa lafiya na musamman suna bukatar su shirya don ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke da cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman masu kula da marasa lafiya.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar sankarar bargo da ba a san dalilinsa ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus ne wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus 2 mai cutar cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A yau, kusan kashi 80 cikin ɗari na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato, kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ciwon huhu ko babu ciwon huhu, kuma yawancinsu suna warkewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari na masu cutar, COVID-19 yana haifar da mummunan rauni wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari na masu cutar ke samun mummunan yanayin cutar wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin ɗari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Ingila (UK), kuma mun kwatanta shi da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK da na Italiya na lokacin daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma halin da annobar COVID-19 ke ciki a sauran duniya yanzu yana kama da na ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurovigilance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta bayar da rahoton mutane uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano wasu mutane da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa 30 na EU/EEA da kuma Ingila (UK) inda, daga 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu mutum 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutum 1,727 da suka mutu, daga cikinsu akwai mutum 17,750 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutum 1,441 da suka mutu a Italiya kadai.
Samun jimlar adadin mutane da ke fama da cutar COVID-19
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana sabunta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga kafofin hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance cigaban COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila, da kuma kwatanta shi da kwarewar Italiya.
Don tantance yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa jimlar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 ta hanyar yin la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Ingila, daga ranar 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma kwatanta jimillar adadin masu cutar da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe da bayanan Italiya na lokacin daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Canjin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Yawan adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila ya yi daidai da na lardin Hubei na China (Hoto na 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya, yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu kafin ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ci gaban ya fi yawa ne saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila sun nuna irin wannan karuwar a cikin yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 (ƙarin bayanai).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna jimillar adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila idan aka kwatanta da bayanan Italiya na lokacin daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An lura cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8:00, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Ingila sun riga sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin masu cutar kamar Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila.
Canjin yanayin cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Kuma wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban kuma akwai bambance-bambance a cikin amsoshin sabis na kiwon lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, bambance-bambance masu yuwuwa a cikin ma'anar shari'a da bambance-bambance a cikin hanyoyin zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun ba da rahoton cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiyar COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da sassan kula da gaggawa a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun cika ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da karɓar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko dakunan kulawa na musamman a halin yanzu suna samuwa a cikin EU/EEA don kashi 6 cikin ɗari da kashi 1 cikin ɗari na masu cutar, bi da bi (ba a gabatar da bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, akwai buƙatar tattara bayanai a kai a kai don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu waɗanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan adadin rahotanni da mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a 201011 ya nuna bambanci mai yawa a cikin adadin gadaje da ke akwai a sassan kulawa na tsakiya da na musamman a Turai, daga gadaje 29.2 ga mutane 100,000 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a Portugal.
Hakan yana nufin cewa ƙasashen suna da ƙarin ko ƙasa da Italiya (12.5 gadaje na kulawa mai tsanani da matsakaici ga kowane mutum 100,000 a 201011).
Ana ba da yanayin samfurin da ya shafi cikawar kulawa, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Ingila na yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti da ke da haɗarin kashi 90% na wucewar ƙarfin gado a cikin ICU, a cikin sabuntawa na shida na kimanta haɗarin haɗarin CEPCM na COVID-19.
Tun da yake har yanzu an tattara cututtuka a wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa galibi suna ɗaukar ƙayyadadden yanki, ya kamata a fi dacewa a tattara bayanan shari'o'i da gadaje a matakin 2 na Ƙididdigar Ƙungiyoyin Ƙasa (NUTS 2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma ci gaban da ake samu a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Ingila.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da sassan kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani dole ne su shirya don yanayin ci gaba da yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman masu kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani, kamar a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken haɗarin CEPCM na kwanan nan, hanzari, aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanya yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, daga hanyar hanawa zuwa ragewa, saboda saurin karuwa da farkon adadin masu cutar na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita amsar su daidai, idan ba a aiwatar da komai ba a gaba.
Binciken haɗarin da aka yi cikin sauri ya kuma nuna matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci da kowace ƙasa za ta iya ƙara ƙarfin ƙoƙarin ta na hana yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar ƙaruwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa, ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta harba mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'in jin kai.
Kamar takwaransa, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da dubban masu cutar SARS a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa ta hanyar bera kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 ba ta da tsanani da mutuwa kamar SARS, amma tana da saurin yaduwa, kuma tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma maza fiye da mata.
A sakamakon haka, mutane da yawa sun soma yin bincike a kan wannan cuta mai tasowa.
Za mu tattauna abubuwa na asali game da cututtuka, cututtuka, cututtuka, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da kuma rigakafin cututtuka.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan binciken zai taimaka wajen fahimtar wannan muguwar cuta da kuma kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya yi tasiri sosai a kan Sinawa, waɗanda aka tilasta su kasance a kulle a cikin makon zinariya da kuma wasu makonni masu tsawo saboda yaduwar sabon cutar kwayar cuta.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) da ta haifar da barkewar cutar SARS a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta kira ta SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ke tattare da ita ana kiranta cutar coronavirus 19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a duk faɗin China kafin ta bazu zuwa kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Har zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da mutane fiye da 80,000 da suka kamu da COVID-19, tare da marasa lafiya sama da 40,000 da aka kwantar a asibiti da kuma mutuwar sama da 3,000.
WHO ta ce COVID-19 ita ce  magabcin jama'a na 1 , mai yuwuwar zama mafi haɗari fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga bincike sama da 200 kan COVID-19, gami da fannonin ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, cututtukan cututtuka, cututtukan cututtuka, ganewar asali da magani, tun lokacin da aka fara bayar da rahoto a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 game da jerin ƙwayoyin cuta, waɗanda aka ware daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan bita ya yi ƙoƙari ya tattara ci gaban bincike a kan wannan sabon batu mai tasowa.
Da zaran mun iya, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wata cuta mai kama da coronavirus, wato Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, wadda ta ɓarke a shekara ta 2012).
Za mu kuma duba abin da muka koya a kan yadda za a hana cutar da kuma yadda za a yi hasashen cutar, kuma za mu tattauna wasu batutuwa da ba a warware ba amma da ake bukatar gaggawa.
An saba ɗaukar coronavirus a matsayin ƙwayoyin cuta marasa mutuwa ga ɗan adam, galibi suna haifar da kusan kashi 15 cikin ɗari na mura 4.
Koyaya, a cikin wannan ƙarni, mun sami cututtukan coronavirus guda biyu masu cutarwa ga ɗan adam, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar cutar da ta fara a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, bi da bi, kafin ya bazu cikin sauri zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da yawan kamuwa da cuta da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu ita ce annobar korona ta uku da ta bulla a tarihin kwanan nan.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Fig. Fig.1,1, an fara bayar da rahoton cutar sankarar bargo a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an gano yadda cutar ta korona ta fito.
A ranar 15 ga Janairun 2020, an samu mutum na farko da ya mutu a Wuhan.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta yadu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa, larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an ba da rahoton cewa wasu ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun kamu da cutar, wanda ke nuna cewa ana iya samun kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an keɓe birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da duk hanyoyin sufuri.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken asibiti na farko game da cutar ya nuna cewa daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, marasa lafiya 21 ne kawai suka taɓa cin kasuwa na abincin teku a Wuhan, wanda ake ganin asalin cutar daga dabba ne da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya a duniya.
A lokacin da aka rubuta wannan rahoton, cutar ta riga ta yadu zuwa dukan ƙasar Sin da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya (Fig. (Fig.2).2).
Yayin da yanayin ke ci gaba cikin sauri, har yanzu ba a san iyakar cutar da kuma tsananin cutar ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken da aka yi a cibiyoyi da yawa da aka yi a kan marasa lafiya 8,866, ciki har da mutane 4,021 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, ya ba da cikakken bayanin annobar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da mutane a kowane zamani, amma mafi yawa a tsakanin shekaru 30 zuwa 65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne kawai suka kasa shekara 20, kuma 14 ne kawai suka kasa shekara 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kamuwa da maza (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ta bazu a cikin gidaje, musamman a lardin Hubei da kuma yankunan da ke kewaye da shi.
Matsakaicin lokacin da ya wuce tsakanin bayyanar cututtuka da ganewar asali na COVID-19 ya kasance kwanaki 5 (2-9).
Matsakaicin lokacin incubation ya kasance kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Matsakaicin lokacin da ya wuce tsakanin bayyanar cututtuka da mutuwa ya kasance kwanaki 9.5 (4.8-13).
Yawan haifuwa na asali (R0) ya kasance 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05) kuma daidaitaccen R0 ya kasance 2.23-4.82.
Yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya karu sosai har zuwa 23 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda ya yi daidai da yawan ƙaura da aka yi kafin bikin bazara a China.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka gano a matsayin tabbataccen lamari ya kasance 1.44% (CI 95%: 1.10-1.86%) da daidaitaccen mutuwar dukkan marasa lafiya ya kasance 3.06% (CI 95%: 2.02-4.59%).
Abubuwa uku da ke haifar da kamuwa da COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), tsufa (≥ 60), da kuma ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
Kwayoyin cutar korona suna cikin ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta masu girma da ke ɗauke da RNA guda.
Ana iya rarraba su zuwa jinsuna huɗu, wato, alpha, beta, gamma, da delta, waɗanda aka sani da cutar coronavirus da ke kamuwa da mutane a cikin jinsunan alpha da beta.
Glycoprotein Spike (S) na ambulaf ya ɗaure da enzyme mai canza angiotensin 2 (ACE2) da dipeptidyl peptidase-4 (DPP4) na masu karɓar kwayoyin halitta don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, bi da bi, sannan haɗuwa da membrane yana faruwa.
Ana sakin kwayar RNA ta kwayar cutar zuwa cikin kwayar halitta; bayan kwayar cutar ta kwayar halitta ta sakewa, kwayar RNA ta kwayar halitta tare da glycoproteins da nucleocapsid sun hada da kwayar halitta da ke dauke da virions, wanda ke haɗuwa da membrane plasma don sakin kwayar cutar.
An gabatar da jerin kwayoyin halittar SARS-CoV-2 na farko a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2020.
An tabbatar da cewa SARS-CoV-2 wani sabon nau'in betacoronavirus ne, tare da fiye da kashi 99.98 cikin ɗari na asalin kwayoyin halitta tsakanin samfuran 10 da aka tattara daga wurin da cutar ta samo asali, kasuwar abincin teku ta Huanan a Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kusa da SARS-CoV fiye da MERS-CoV.
Ta amfani da na'urar duban dan adam ta lantarki, an gano wasu ƙwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin ƙananan sassan jikin mutum na numfashi.
An gano cewa mutum ACE2 mai karɓar SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure da ACE2 na ɗan adam da ƙarancin ƙarfi fiye da na SARS-CoV, wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da ƙarancin kamuwa da cuta fiye da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya samar da sabon ɗan gajeren furotin da aka tsara ta hanyar lorf3b da kuma furotin mai ɓoyewa wanda aka tsara ta hanyar lorf8.
Lorf3b na SARS-CoV-2 na iya taka rawa wajen cutar kwayar cuta da hana lIFNβ bayyanawa; duk da haka, lorf8 ba shi da sanannun yankuna ko alamu na aiki.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, et al. sun nuna tsarin cryo-ME na cikakken ɗan adam ACE2 a ƙuduri na 2.9 Å a cikin hadaddun tare da mai jigilar amino acid B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa hadaddun, wanda ke da fasalin buɗewa da rufewa, an haɗa shi a matsayin dimer kuma hadaddun ACE2-B0AT1 na iya ɗaure sunadarai biyu na S, wanda ke ba da alamomi don ganewa da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus.
B0AT1 na iya zama maƙasudin magani don tantance magunguna don kawar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2.
Mai watsa shiri na asali da mai watsa shiri na tsakiya
An gano cewa SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV sun samo asali ne daga bera kuma an watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar civets da camelliids, bi da bi.
Bayan kwatanta kwayoyin halittar SARS-CoV-2 da sauran cututtukan coronavirus, an gabatar da bera a matsayin mai karɓar SARS-CoV-2 na asali, saboda sabon kwayar cutar ta kasance daidai da kashi 96 cikin ɗari tare da nau'ikan SARS-CoVs guda biyu daga bera da ake kira bat-SL-CoVZX45 da bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Duk da haka, ba a san ko wane mai watsa shiri ne ya ba da damar cutar ta ƙetare shingen jinsuna don ya kamu da mutane ba, kuma ba a san hanyar watsawa ba tukuna.
Ji, et al., sun yi hasashen cewa cutar ta iya yaduwa daga bera zuwa mutum ta hanyar macizai, wanda ke nuna sake haɗuwa a cikin furotin S.
