Koyaya, coronavirus na iya hana ayyukan ƙwayoyin T ta hanyar haifar da apoptosis.
Ƙarfin jiki na jiki, tare da ƙarin abubuwa kamar C3a da C5a da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta, yana da muhimmanci wajen yaƙi da kamuwa da ƙwayoyin cuta.
Alal misali, ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga mai haƙuri da ya warke sun kawar da MERS-CoV.
A wani ɓangare kuma, idan jikinmu ya yi tsayayya da cutar, za mu iya samun ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa, kuma hakan zai iya sa huhu da sauran gabobin jikinmu su lalace sosai.
Cutar SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke faruwa a gida, tana iya shafar tsofaffi da ke fama da cututtuka da yawa da kuma mata masu ciki.
An yarda cewa mutanen da ke fama da ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa ko kuma waɗanda ke da ƙarancin aikin rigakafi suna cikin haɗarin kamuwa da cutar fiye da sauran mutane.
An kiyasta matsakaicin lokacin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance daga kwana 1 zuwa 14, amma yawanci daga kwana 3 zuwa 7 bisa ga binciken da aka yi kan mutane 425 da aka fara gano a Wuhan.
Duk da haka, binciken da aka yi kan mutane 1099 ya nuna cewa tsawon lokacin kamuwa da cutar ya kai kwanaki 3 a matsakaita, daga kwanaki 0 zuwa 24.
Wani sabon bincike, kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, ya kammala da tsawon lokacin incubation na kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2) bisa ga yawan mutane 8,866.
Yana da matukar muhimmanci hukumomin kiwon lafiya su daidaita tsawon lokacin keɓewa bisa ga lokacin ɓoyewa daidai gwargwado, don hana mutane masu kamuwa da cutar amma ba su da alamun cutar daga watsa kwayar cutar.
A yawancin lokaci, ana keɓe mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ko kuma waɗanda suka kamu da ita na kwanaki 14.
Shin ya kamata a tsawaita keɓewar zuwa kwanaki 24?
Sau da yawa zazzabi ne farkon kuma babban alamar COVID-19, kuma yana iya kasancewa ko ba ya tare da wasu alamomi kamar tari mai bushewa, numfashi, ciwon tsoka, zafin jiki, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, hanci, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya da amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami dyspnea da/ko hypoxemia mako guda bayan cutar ta fara.
A cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani, sun soma ciwon numfashi, ciwon ƙwayar cuta, ƙwayar cuta da kuma ciwon jini.
Masu fama da zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi da masu fama da zazzabi mai tsanani, koda babu wani abu mara kyau a cikin radiography na kirji, ya kamata a gwada su don cutar don saurin ganewa.
Wani bincike da aka yi a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna da zazzabi, kashi 76 cikin ɗari na tari mai bushe, kashi 55 cikin ɗari na numfashi, da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na zawo; kashi 8 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya sun bukaci taimakon numfashi.
An samu irin wannan binciken a cikin binciken biyu da aka yi kwanan nan da aka yi a kan iyali da kuma wani ciwo da ya faru bayan kamuwa da cutar daga mutum marar alamun cutar.
Hakazalika, binciken yawan jama'a da aka yi a shekara ta 2012 ya nuna cewa manyan alamun cututtukan marasa lafiya da ke da MERS-CoV sune zazzabi (98%) da tari mai bushe (47%) da kuma numfashi mai wuya (55%).
Koyaya, kashi 80 cikin ɗari sun buƙaci taimakon numfashi, wanda ya fi na marasa lafiya da COVID-19, wanda ya dace da yawan mutuwar MERS idan aka kwatanta da COVID-19.
An kuma lura da gudawa (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiyar MERS.
A game da SARS, an gano cewa manyan alamun cutar zazzabi ne (99%-100%), tari mai bushe (29%-75%), numfashi (40%-42%), zawo (20%-25%) da ciwon makogwaro (13%-25%) kuma ana buƙatar taimakon numfashi ga kusan kashi 14-20% na marasa lafiya.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, yawan mutanen da COVID-19 ya kashe ya kai kashi 2 cikin ɗari, inda aka samu mutane 66,576 da suka kamu da cutar a duniya.
Idan aka gwada, mutuwar SARS a watan Nuwamba 2002 ya kai kashi 10 cikin ɗari a cikin mutane 8,096 da aka tabbatar da cutar.
A cikin MERS, a cewar wani binciken yawan jama'a da aka yi a watan Yunin 2012, mutuwar ta kai kashi 37 cikin ɗari a cikin mutane 2,494 da aka tabbatar da cutar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a baya ya nuna cewa R0 na SARS-CoV-2 ya kai 6.47 tare da 95% dogara (CI) na 5.71-7.23, yayin da R0 na SARS-CoV ya kai 2 zuwa 4.
An kwatanta alamun cututtuka, mutuwar da R0 na SARS-CoV-2, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV a cikin Tebur Tebur1.1.
Bayanai da ke sama sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da ƙarfin yaduwa fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV, amma ba ya kashe mutane sosai.
Saboda haka, yana da wuya a sarrafa barkewar SARS-CoV-2 fiye da barkewar MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV.
Sau da yawa ana samun cutar a cikin iyali ko kuma a wurin taro ko kuma a cikin mota, kamar a jirgin ruwa.
Sau da yawa marasa lafiya sun yi tafiya ko zama a Wuhan ko wasu yankuna da cutar ta shafa, ko kuma sun kasance tare da mutane masu cutar ko marasa lafiya a cikin makonni biyu kafin bayyanar cututtuka.
Koyaya, an nuna cewa mutane na iya ɗaukar kwayar cutar ba tare da nuna alamomi ba sama da makonni biyu kuma marasa lafiya da suka warke na iya sake ɗaukar kwayar cutar, wanda ke nuna buƙatar ƙara tsawon lokacin keɓewa.
Marasa lafiya suna da ƙarancin ƙwayoyin farin jini (musamman ƙwayoyin lymphocytes) a farkon matakan.
Alal misali, an gano cutar lymphopenia da ke da adadin farin jini 4 × 109/L da kuma adadin lymphocytes 1 × 109/L, da kuma yawan aspartate aminotransferase da kuma cutar cutar jini a cikin marasa lafiya 1,099 da ke da COVID-19.
Wasu marasa lafiya suna da ƙwayoyin enzymes na hanta, ƙwayoyin enzymes na muscle da myoglobin a cikin jini, kuma mafi yawan suna da ƙwayoyin C-reactive da ƙwayoyin red cell.
A cikin mutane da suka fi ciwo, yawan sinadarin D-dimer da ke cikin jini yana ƙaruwa kuma ƙwayoyin jini suna raguwa.
Ana ganin rashin daidaito a cikin hotunan kirji a yawancin marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19, wanda ke nuna inuwa mara daidaituwa ta ɓangarorin biyu ko kuma rashin haske a cikin gilashin da aka cire a cikin huhu.
Sau da yawa marasa lafiya suna kamuwa da ciwon huhu, ciwon huhu mai tsanani da kuma ciwon numfashi mai tsanani (ADRS).
A wani lokaci, ciwon ƙanƙara yana sa jiki ya ƙone sosai kuma ya riƙa ɗumbin ruwa a jikin mutum.
Rashin aiki na nau'in ƙwayoyin huhu na I da na II yana haifar da raguwar matakin surfactant da ƙaruwa a cikin ƙarfin jiki, don haka rage ƙarfin huhu don kumbura da haɓaka haɗarin rushewar huhu.
Saboda haka, idan aka yi wa mutum gwajin kirji, yakan yi daidai da yanayin da ya fi muni.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, gwajin farko na cutar COVID-19 ya nuna ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu, samar da ƙwayoyin hyaline, shiga cikin ƙwayoyin lymphocyte na ciki da kuma ƙwayoyin syncytial multinuclear a cikin huhu na wani mai haƙuri da ya mutu daga cutar, wanda ya dace da cutar kwayar cuta da SDRA kuma yayi kama da na marasa lafiya da SARS da MERS.
An yi amfani da gano SARS-CoV-2 RNA ta hanyar maganin polymerase chain reaction bayan sake rubutun (RT-PCR) a matsayin babban ma'auni don gano COVID-19.
Duk da haka, saboda yawan ƙarancin ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta, wanda zai iya sa cutar ta yi saurin yaduwa, an fara amfani da bayyanar cututtuka don ganewar asali (wanda a lokacin ya dogara da RT-PCR kawai) a China a ranar 13 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
An lura da irin wannan yanayin don ganewar asali na SARS.
Saboda haka, haɗuwa da tarihin lafiyar mutum, bayyanar cututtuka, gwaje-gwaje na dakin gwaje-gwaje, da kuma gwajin radiology yana da muhimmanci kuma yana da muhimmanci wajen gano cutar.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyar Feng Zhang ta bayyana wata hanyar amfani da fasaha ta SHERLOCK da ke da tushen CRISPR don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke ba da damar gano ɓangarorin RNA na SARS-CoV-2 tsakanin 20 × 10-18 mol/L da 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kwafi a kowane microlit na samfurin) ta amfani da madaurin amsawa a cikin ƙasa da awa ɗaya, ba tare da buƙatar kayan aiki masu ƙwarewa ba.
Ana sa ran wannan sabuwar hanyar za ta inganta ƙwarewa da amfani sosai idan ta kasance mai amfani a kan samfuran asibiti.
Saboda rashin gogewa game da sabon coronavirus, likitoci na iya ba da tallafi ne kawai ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, yayin da suke gwada magungunan da aka riga aka yi amfani da su ko kuma aka ba da shawarar don magance wasu coronavirus, kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, da sauran cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta (Table (Table2).2).
Irin wannan magani ya haɗa da maganin riga-kafi da na gaba da magungunan hana yaduwar cuta, magungunan hana kamuwa da cuta, magungunan steroid, jini na marasa lafiya da suka warke, maganin kasar Sin da kuma taimakon tunani.
Har jini na marasa lafiya da suka warke ma an ba da shi don magani.
Kamfanonin ƙwayoyi suna aiki don samar da rigakafi da alluran rigakafi don cutar.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kai hari ga huhu da farko kuma mai yiwuwa ma, a cikin ƙananan, wasu gabobin da ke nuna ACE2, kamar tsarin hanji da kodan.
Duk da haka, rashin aiki da kuma rashin numfashi ne ainihin abin da ke jawo mutuwa ga marasa lafiya.
Don haka, taimakon numfashi yana da muhimmanci wajen rage alamun cutar da ceton rayuka, wanda ya haɗa da maganin oxygen na gaba ɗaya, maganin oxygen mai saurin gudu, numfashi mara saurin shiga ciki da kuma numfashi mai saurin shiga ciki, dangane da tsananin cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke fama da mummunan alamun numfashi ya kamata su sami iskar oxygen ta hanyar membrane (EMO), wata hanyar canzawar zuciya da huhu da ake amfani da ita don magance ciwon zuciya ko rashin ƙarfi na numfashi.
Bugu da ƙari, kiyaye daidaiton wutan lantarki, hanawa da magance cututtukan na biyu da bugun jini, da kare ayyukan gabobin rayuwa ma suna da mahimmanci ga marasa lafiya da ke da SARS-CoV-2.
An tabbatar da cewa yawan amsawar tsarin garkuwar jiki yana haifar da harin cytokine a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da SARS da MERS.
Cytokine shock wani nau'i ne na amsawar kumburi na tsarin da aka nuna ta hanyar sakin jerin cytokines, gami da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ da MCP-1.
Waɗannan kwayoyin suna sa ƙwayoyin jikinmu su saki ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa, waɗanda suke haddasa cutar ADRS da kuma rashin aiki.
Maganin rigakafi yana da mahimmanci wajen magance tashin hankali na cytokine, musamman ga manyan lokuta.
An yi amfani da corticosteroids da tocilizumab, kwayar cutar rigakafin IL6 mai ƙarancin ƙwayar cuta don magance tashin hankali na cytokine.
Sauran maganin rigakafi na cytokine sun haɗa da daidaitawar amsawar rigakafi ta T-cell, toshe IFN-γ, IL-1, da TNF cytokines, hana JAK, blinatumomab, mai hana siginar cytokine 4, da masu hana HDAC.
Ana amfani da kwayoyin steroid a matsayin masu hana rigakafi a cikin maganin SARS don rage tsananin cutar kumburi.
Koyaya, shan magungunan steroid masu yawa ba su da tasiri mai amfani akan mummunan lalacewar huhu a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da SARS da COVID-19.
Maimakon haka, suna iya haifar da mummunan sakamako, ciki har da cutar ƙwayoyin cuta, wanda hakan ke shafar yanayin cutar sosai.
Duk da haka, an ba da shawarar yin amfani da gajeren lokaci na ƙananan allurai na corticosteroids a hankali ga marasa lafiya da ke da mummunan COVID-19.
A lokacin da aka rubuta wannan rahoton, babu wani magani mai tasiri wanda aka tabbatar.
Koyaya, shan remdesivir a cikin jijiya, wanda yake kama da nucleoside, ya tabbatar da inganci a cikin wani mai cutar COVID-19 na Amurka.
Remdesivir wani sabon magani ne na rigakafin ƙwayoyin cuta wanda Gilead ta fara samarwa don maganin cututtukan da ƙwayoyin cuta na Ebola da Marburg ke haifarwa.
Daga baya, remdesivir ya kuma nuna yiwuwar hana wasu ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya, ciki har da MERS da SARS.
Bisa ga waɗannan binciken, Gilead ta tura mahaɗin zuwa China don ba da damar gwaji da yawa akan mutane da ke da cutar SARS-CoV-2, kuma ana sa ran sakamakon sosai.
Bugu da ƙari, baricitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir da ribavirin an gabatar da su azaman yiwuwar jiyya ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da cututtukan numfashi.
Za a iya samun zawo, tashin zuciya, amai, lalacewar hanta da sauran cututtuka sakamakon maganin haɗin lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Ya kamata a kula da hulɗar waɗannan magungunan tare da wasu magungunan da ake amfani da su a cikin marasa lafiya.
Jinin marasa lafiya da suka warke da kuma samar da rigakafi
