Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19 (cuta da cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa) a matsayin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar  annoba  tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu ne kawai, ba yadda hatsarin ke da shi ba, WHO ta nuna bukatar tilasta wa gwamnatoci su ɗauki mataki:
 Duk ƙasashe suna iya canja yanayin annobar.
Idan ƙasashe sun gano, gwada, bi da, ware, ganowa da kuma tattara jama'arsu a matsayin wani ɓangare na amsawar , in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
 Muna da damuwa sosai, ba kawai game da yawan yaduwar cutar da kuma yadda ta tsananta ba, amma kuma game da rashin aiki. 
A cewar Dr. Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Amurka, annobar  ba ta taɓa faruwa ba .
Ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu cewa  banda mura, babu wani kwayar cutar numfashi da aka gano tun lokacin da ta fara har zuwa lokacin da ta ci gaba da yaduwa a duniya. 
Ghebreyesus ya nuna irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa  ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da cutar coronavirus ta haifar ba. 
Ya kara da cewa: "Ba mu taba ganin annoba da za a iya sarrafa ta a lokaci guda ba".
Sabon matsayin annobar ya biyo bayan shawarar da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yanke a watan Janairu ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta duniya.
Daraktan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da ke Shafar Mutane a Amirka, Dokta Anthony Fauci ya ce game da annobar: "A takaice dai, yanayin zai daɗa muni".
A ranar Alhamis, Associated Press ta ba da rahoton cewa akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da COVID-19 a duniya, kuma fiye da 4,600 sun mutu.
Annobar cutar korona ta 2019-20 annobar cutar korona ce da ke ci gaba tun daga shekarar 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar coronavirus mai tsanani ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ke haifarwa.
An gano annobar a Wuhan, China a watan Disamba na 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a a duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020 kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Har zuwa 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an samu kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da COVID-19 a ƙasashe 210 da yankuna, kuma kusan mutane 97,000 sun mutu.
Mutane kusan 364,000 ne suka warke.
An kiyasta yawan mutuwar a China ya kai kashi 4 cikin ɗari, yayin da a sauran duniya ya bambanta daga kashi 13.04 cikin ɗari a Aljeriya zuwa kashi 0.08 cikin ɗari a New Zealand.
Alamun cututtuka na yau da kullum sun haɗa da zazzabi, tari da kuma numfashi.
Matsaloli na iya haɗa da ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Yawancin lokaci lokaci tsakanin kamuwa da cutar da bayyanar cututtuka kusan kwanaki biyar ne, amma zai iya zama tsakanin kwanaki biyu zuwa 14.
Babu wani rigakafi ko magani na musamman da aka sani.
Babban magani shine maganin alamun cuta da tallafi. Matakan rigakafin da aka ba da shawarar sun haɗa da wanke hannu, rufe baki don tari, nisantawa da wasu mutane, da saka idanu da kuma keɓe waɗanda ake zargi da kamuwa da cutar.
Hukumomi a duk faɗin duniya sun amsa ta hanyar kafa takunkumin tafiya, keɓewa, dokar hana fita, sarrafa haɗari a wuraren aiki da rufe cibiyoyi.
Cutar ta haifar da mummunan rikicewar zamantakewar tattalin arziki a duniya, jinkirta ko soke wasanni, addini, siyasa da al'adu, da kuma ƙarancin abinci da aka ƙara ta hanyar sayayya.
Makarantu da jami'o'i sun rufe a ƙasashe 193 ko kuma a yankuna, wanda ya shafi kusan kashi 99.4 na ɗaliban duniya.
Labaran karya game da cutar sun bazu a intanet, kuma akwai ƙiyayya da nuna bambanci ga Sinawa, da sauran mutanen da suka fito daga Gabas da Kudu maso Gabashin Asiya da kuma waɗanda suka zo daga yankunan da ke da yawan kamuwa da cutar.
Saboda raguwar tafiye-tafiye da rufewa a masana'antar nauyi, an sami raguwar gurɓatar iska da fitar da carbon.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya a Wuhan, China (babban birnin lardin Hubei) sun ba da rahoton wani ciwo na ciwon huhu da ba a san dalilinsa ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma an fara bincike a farkon Janairu, 2020.
Yawancin masu cutar sun kasance a kasuwar sayar da abincin teku ta Huanan, saboda haka ana tsammanin cutar ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi.
Kwayar cutar da ta haifar da annobar ana kiranta SARS-CoV-2, kwayar cutar da aka gano kwanan nan kuma tana da alaƙa da coronavirus na bera, pangolin coronavirus, da SARS-CoV. Daga baya, an gano cewa mutum na farko da aka sani da alamun cutar ya kamu da rashin lafiya a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma wannan mutumin ba shi da wata alaƙa da bayyanar cutar daga baya a kasuwar kayan sabo.
Daga cikin masu cutar da aka fara ganowa a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku sun kasance masu alaƙa da kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba a jaridar South China Morning Post ya nuna cewa ana iya samun mutum na farko da cutar a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, wanda ke da shekara 55 a lardin Hubei. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa, yayin da sabbin masu cutar ke raguwa a China amma ba zato ba tsammani suna ƙaruwa a Italiya, Iran, da Koriya ta Kudu, yawan sabbin masu cutar a wajen China ya zarce adadin sabbin masu cutar a China a karon farko.
Za a iya ƙididdige yawan masu cutar, musamman waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya.
A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta a tsakanin matasa, waɗanda shekarunsu ba su kai 19 ba sun kai kashi 2.4 cikin ɗari na masu cutar a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60 cikin ɗari na mutanen Burtaniya dole ne su kamu da cutar kafin su sami rigakafin garken da ya dace.
Cutar ta shafi yawan mutanen da aka gwada su da COVID-19 kuma aka tabbatar da sun kamu da cutar bisa ga ƙa'idodin hukuma.
Har zuwa 23 ga watan Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na yawanta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa suna da manufofin hukuma na ba da gwaji ga waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka buga a ranar 16 ga watan Maris ya nuna cewa a China, har zuwa 23 ga watan Janairu, an kiyasta kashi 86 cikin ɗari na masu kamuwa da COVID-19 ba a gano su ba, kuma waɗannan kamuwa da cutar da ba a yi rajista da su ba ne tushen kamuwa da kashi 79 cikin ɗari na masu kamuwa da cutar.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka buga a ranar 30 ga Maris ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya ya fi na waɗanda aka ruwaito yawa.
