Waɗannan ƙididdigar sun bambanta tsakanin yankuna da lokaci, kuma ana rinjayar su da yawan gwaje-gwaje, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan magani, tsawon lokacin da cutar ta fara, da kuma yanayin alƙaluma kamar shekaru, jinsi, kuma musamman lafiyar jiki.
