Za a iya kashe ƙwayoyin cuta ta hanyoyi da yawa (a cikin minti ɗaya na fallasa maganin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta don farfajiyar ƙarfe), ciki har da 62% ethanol, isopropanol, 50%, sodium hypochlorite, 0.1%, hydrogen peroxide, 0.5%, da povidone iodine, 0.2%, 7.5%.
Wasu magunguna kamar su benzalkonium chloride da chlorhexidine gluconate ba su da amfani sosai.
