Amsar da Birtaniya ta bayar ga cutar ta fara bayyana a matsayin daya daga cikin mafi sassauci a cikin ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa, kuma har zuwa 18 ga Maris, 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta sanya wani nau'i na nisantar jama'a ko kuma ta sanya mazauna cikin keɓewa ba.
