A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya rattaba hannu kan Dokar Ƙarin Kuɗaɗen Shirye-shiryen Cutar Korona da Amsa, wanda ke samar da kuɗin gaggawa na dala biliyan 8.3 don taimakawa hukumomin tarayya wajen magance annobar.
Kamfanoni sun hana ma'aikatansu tafiya, sun soke taron taro kuma sun ƙarfafa ma'aikatansu su yi aiki daga gida.
An soke abubuwan wasanni da lokutan wasanni. A ranar 11 ga Maris, Trump ya sanar da hana tafiye-tafiye ga yawancin Turai, ban da Burtaniya, na kwanaki 30 daga ranar 13 ga Maris.
Kashegari, ya faɗaɗa ƙuntatawa zuwa Ƙasar Ingila da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci ta kasa, wanda ya samar da kudaden tarayya don magance matsalar.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga watan Maris, kamfanoni da yawa sun rufe ko rage lokacin aiki a duk faɗin Amurka don ƙoƙarin hana yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da barkewar cutar a kowace jiha 50 da gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an samu mutum 10,700 da suka kamu da cutar korona a birnin New York, wanda ya fi yawan mutanen da ke Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, gwamnan ya ce nisantar da mutane da jama'a kamar tana aiki ne yayin da ƙididdigar ninki biyu na masu cutar ta tashi daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da mutane 32,308 da cutar a New York City, kuma mutane 672 sun mutu. A ranar 26 ga Maris, Amurka ta ba da rahoton mutane da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya. A ranar 8 ga Afrilu, an tabbatar da mutane 400,335 da cutar a Amurka, kuma mutane 12,841 sun mutu.
A ranar 30 ga watan Maris, ta hanyar manema labarai, Shugaban Amurka Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita umarnin nisantar jama'a har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu.
A wannan ranar, jirgin ruwan asibiti mai gadaje 1,000 mai suna USNS Comfort ya sauka a birnin New York.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, Amurka ta samu mutuwar mutum 884 sakamakon cutar korona a cikin sa'o'i 24.
A jihar New York, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya wuce 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki Fadar White House don rage girman barazanar da kuma sarrafa sadarwa ta hanyar umarci jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya su daidaita bayanan jama'a da wallafe-wallafe game da cutar tare da ofishin Mataimakin Shugaban Mike Pence.
A cikin wannan lokacin, akwai wasu bangarori da suka nuna rashin amincewarsu da yadda Trump ya magance matsalar.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki dogaro da Amurka kan shigo da kayayyakin aiki, musamman na'urorin kiwon lafiya, daga China.
An yi amfani da nazarin yanayin tafiye-tafiyen jirgin sama don zana taswira da hasashen yanayin yaduwar, kuma an buga shi a cikin Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar Janairu 2020.
Bisa ga rahoton 2018 na Ƙungiyar Jiragen Sama ta Duniya, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo da Taipei sun fi yawan matafiya daga Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney da Melbourne ma sanannun wurare ne ga mutanen da ke barin Wuhan.
Bali an ɗauka a matsayin mafi ƙarancin ƙwarewa a cikin shahararrun biranen 20 na masu zuwa don shiri, yayin da aka ɗauki biranen Ostiraliya sun fi dacewa. Ostiraliya ta fitar da shirin gaggawa na sabon coronavirus (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
Ya nuna cewa har yanzu akwai abubuwa da yawa da za a gano game da COVID-19 kuma Australia za ta ƙara ƙarfafa kula da kan iyakoki da sadarwa a cikin aikinta na magance cutar.
A ranar 21 ga watan Maris, an ayyana gaggawa ta lafiyar ɗan adam a Ostiraliya.
Saboda keɓewar sufuri na jama'a daga Wuhan da Hubei, ƙasashe da dama sun shirya kwashe 'yan ƙasa da ma'aikatan diflomasiyya daga yankin, galibi ta jiragen da ƙasar ta yi hayar su, tare da izinin hukumomin China.
Kasashen Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Ostareliya, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus da Thailand sun kasance cikin ƙasashe na farko da suka fara kwashe 'yan ƙasarsu.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta kwashe 'yan kasar ta daga China ba.
A ranar 7 ga watan Fabrairu, Brazil ta kwashe 'yan Brazil 34 ko danginsu da kuma 'yan Poland huɗu, da wani ɗan China da kuma wani ɗan Indiya.
'Yan kasar Poland, China da Indiya sun sauka a Poland, inda jirgin na Brazil ya tsaya kafin ya ci gaba da tafiya zuwa Brazil.
An killace 'yan ƙasar Brazil da suka ziyarci Wuhan a wani sansanin soji kusa da Brasília.
A ranar, an kwashe 'yan Kanada 215 (mutanen 176 a cikin jirgin farko da 39 a cikin jirgin sama na biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi hayar) daga Wuhan zuwa BFC Trenton don keɓewa na makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama mai dauke da 'yan Kanada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a BFC Trenton.
Hukumomin Australia sun kwashe 'yan ƙasa 277 a ranakun 3 da 4 ga watan Fabrairu zuwa cibiyar tsare mutane a tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka mai da shi wurin keɓewa, inda suka zauna na kwanaki 14.
Jirgin sama na kwashe mutane daga New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu; an killace fasinjojinsa (musamman daga Australia da Pacific) a sansanin jiragen ruwa na Whangaparaoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga watan Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar cewa za ta kwashe Amurkawa a cikin jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, jirgin da ke ɗauke da fasinjojin Kanada 129 da aka kwashe daga jirgin Diamond Princess ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasar ta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga Maris, jirgin saman South African Airways da gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi hayar ya dawo da 'yan Afirka ta Kudu 112.
An yi gwajin lafiya kafin tashi kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu da ke nuna alamun cutar coronavirus a wurin don rage haɗarin.
Sai kawai 'yan Afirka ta Kudu da gwajin su ya nuna ba su da lafiya ne aka mayar da su gida.
Sakamakon gwajin ya ba da izinin duk 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin agaji, waɗanda, a matsayin matakin kariya, duk sun kasance a cikin kulawa da keɓewa na kwanaki 14 a Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye wasu dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Waje ta kasar Sin ta ce kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun aika da taimako zuwa kasar Sin.
Wasu ɗaliban Sinawa da ke karatun jami'o'in Amurka sun haɗu don taimakawa wajen aika taimako zuwa yankunan da cutar ta shafa na China, tare da ƙungiyar haɗin gwiwa daga yankin Greater Chicago da aka ba da rahoton cewa ta aika da abin rufe fuska N95 50,000 zuwa asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu. Ƙungiyar agaji ta Direct Relief, tare da haɗin gwiwar FedEx, ta aika da abin rufe fuska 200,000 da sauran kayan kariya na mutum, gami da safar hannu da riguna, ta hanyar gaggawa ta iska zuwa Asibitin Union na Wuhan a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa binciken allurar rigakafi da ƙoƙarin magani da kare  mutanen da ke cikin haɗari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya .
Interaksiyon ta ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta aika da tallafin da ya kai dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da takunkumin rufe fuska miliyan 1 ga Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da sama da tan 13 na kayan aikin likita zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da ba da hannayen riga na likita miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayan aikin likita daban-daban ciki har da Hazmat su 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da tan 17.8 na kayan aikin likita ga China kuma ta yi alkawarin ƙarin dala miliyan 100 na tallafin kuɗi ga ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa. Da zarar an daidaita lamura a China, ƙasar ta aika da taimako ga ƙasashe da dama da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayan aikin likita da masana don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance annobar coronavirus.
Wani dan kasuwa mai suna Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da rigunan kariya 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha don tarayyar Afirka ta rarraba su.
Daga baya ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, abin rufe fuska 100,000 da na'urorin numfashi 5 zuwa Panama.
Ma ya kuma ba da kayan aikin likita ga Kanada. Kasashen Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwa game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwaji da aka yi a China.
Alal misali, Spain ta janye kayan gwaji na korona 58,000 da aka yi a China da ya yi daidai da kashi 30 cikin ɗari kawai, yayin da Netherlands ta dawo da abin rufe fuska 600,000 na kasar Sin da suka lalace.
Belgium ta dawo da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, wanda ake zaton sun fito ne daga China, amma a gaskiya sun fito ne daga Colombia.
A wani bangare kuma, an yi maraba da taimakon da kasar Sin ta bayar a yankunan Latin Amurka da Afirka.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi wajen sarrafa da kuma dakile annobar.
WHO ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin China da ɓoyewa da hana ƙoƙarin rigakafi da hanawa, da rikicin yanzu inda gwamnatin tsakiya  ta ba da rahotanni na yau da kullun don hana firgici a jajibirin Sabuwar Shekarar Lunar .
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a lokacin da ya amsa shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na hana tafiya daga Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya nuna cewa ko da yake wannan ba shawarar WHO ba ce, amma wata muhimmiyar alama ce ta sadaukar da kai ga hana barkewar cutar a inda ta fi yawa kuma ya yi magana game da abin da ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin kiwon lafiyar jama'a. A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da yaduwar cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum a China da kuma karuwar mutane a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta duniya (USPPI), matakin na 10 da aka ɗauka tun lokacin annobar mura ta 2009.
Darakta Janar na WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce USPPI ya samo asali ne daga hadarin yaduwar cutar a duniya, musamman ga ƙasashe masu karamin kuɗi da masu matsakaitan kuɗi ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
A cikin martani ga dokar hana tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya ce:  babu dalilin da zai sa a hana tafiye-tafiye da kasuwanci na duniya  kuma  WHO ba ta ba da shawarar hana kasuwanci da tafiye-tafiye .
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da dala miliyan 675 don tallafawa shirye-shiryen da ake yi a ƙasashe masu karamin kuɗi, ta nuna cewa akwai bukatar gaggawa don tallafa wa ƙasashen da  ba su da tsarin da ya dace don gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, ko da yake cutar ta kusa bayyana .
Tedros ya ci gaba da cewa muna  kamar yadda muke da ƙarfi kamar yadda muke da rauni  kuma ya aririci al'ummar duniya  su saka hannun jari a yau  ko kuma su biya ƙarin gobe . A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana a wani taron manema labarai cewa cutar tana da sunan COVID-19.
A wannan rana, Tedros ya ce Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da haɗa  ƙarfin dukan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cikin amsa .
Don haka an kunna ƙungiyar kula da rikice-rikice ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, don daidaita dukkanin amsar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar  mai da hankali kan amsar kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomin za su iya ba da ƙwarewar su don magance tasirin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da ci gaban cutar .
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, an tura tawagar aikin hadin gwiwa ta WHO zuwa China don tura masana na duniya da WHO zuwa China don tallafawa gudanar da aikin ƙasa da kuma tantance  tsananin cutar da yaduwar cutar  ta hanyar gudanar da bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin ƙasa da kuma gudanar da ziyarar ƙasa don tantance  tasirin ayyukan amsawa a larduna da gundumomi, gami da birane da karkara . A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ce  duniya ta kamata ta yi ƙarin shirye-shirye don cutar coronavirus , tana mai nuna cewa  ko da yake ba a daɗe ba don yin magana game da cutar, duk da haka kowace ƙasa  ya kamata ta shiga cikin shirin .
Dangane da ci gaban annobar a Iran, WHO ta tura ƙungiyar haɗin gwiwa don tantance yanayin. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce ƙimar barazanar coronavirus a duniya ta tashi daga  mai girma  zuwa  mai girma , matakin gargadi da ƙimar haɗari mafi girma.
Mike Ryan, darektan shirin kula da gaggawa na lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadi a cikin wata sanarwa cewa: "Wannan ya zama abin da ya kamata ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: farka.
Wataƙila cutar tana kan hanyarsa kuma kuna buƙatar kasancewa a shirye , yana ƙara cewa matakan da suka dace na iya taimaka wa duniya ta guji  mafi munin .
Ryan ya ci gaba da cewa bayanan da ake da su yanzu ba sa ba jami'an kiwon lafiya damar sanar da annobar duniya, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar na nufin cewa  mun yarda da cewa kowane mutum a duniya yana fuskantar cutar .
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, WHO ta ce za a iya kiran annobar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO  tana da matukar damuwa game da yadda cutar ke yaduwa da kuma tsanani da kuma yadda ba a kula da cutar . WHO ta fuskanci zargi mai tsanani game da yadda ta gudanar da annobar, wanda aka ce bai dace ba, musamman saboda jinkirin sanar da gaggawa na lafiyar jama'a da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annobar.
Wannan mummunan martani ya samu goyon baya daga wata takarda mai neman babban darektan WHO Tedros Adhanom ya yi murabus, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, masana da dama kan hakkin bil'adama na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun mai da hankali kan girmama haƙƙin kowane mutum a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce kowa na da hakkin samun agajin gaggawa kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin hakan.
Ƙungiyar ta nace cewa rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya ba za su taɓa zama hujja ba don nuna bambanci ga wani rukuni na musamman.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowane mutum yana da hakkin samun lafiya, gami da nakasassu, 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, mutanen da aka kora daga gidajensu, marasa gida, waɗanda ke cikin matsanancin talauci, fursunoni, da 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyin da ba a ambata ba waɗanda ke buƙatar tallafin gwamnati.
Ƙungiyoyin gwamnati na duniya suna kula da tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar al'umma na rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar Tattalin Arziki ta Ƙasa ta ƙaddamar da wani dandamali wanda ke ba da cikakken bayani game da yadda ake magance matsalolin siyasa a ƙasashe daban-daban a duniya, da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Daga manufofi don ƙarfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya da kuma amsawa ga tasirin kullewa da ƙuntatawa na tafiya, dandamali na dijital ya haɗa da kayan aikin bin diddigin manufofin ƙasa don taimakawa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da sauƙaƙe daidaitaccen martani na duniya ga ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Gwamnatin China ta sha suka daga Amurka, Ministan Ofishin Ministan Birtaniya Michael Gove da dan Shugaban Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, kan yadda ta gudanar da annobar, wadda ta fara a lardin Hubei na China.
An cire wasu shugabannin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CCP) daga mukaman su sakamakon yadda suka gudanar da dokar killacewa a tsakiyar kasar Sin, a matsayin wata alama ta rashin jin daɗi game da yadda jami'an siyasa ke amsa cutar a yankunan.
Wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa an yi wannan ne don kare babban sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a game da annobar coronavirus.
Wasu manyan jami'an kasar Sin, kamar Zhao Lijian, sun yi watsi da ra'ayin farko cewa annobar coronavirus ta fara ne a Wuhan don su goyi bayan ra'ayoyin makirci cewa COVID-19 ta samo asali ne daga Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin Donald Trump ta Amurka ta kira coronavirus  kwayar cutar China  ko  kwayar cutar Wuhan , tana cewa  a China  ƙuntatawa ta ƙara cutar da ta zama annoba ta duniya , wanda daga baya wasu masu adawa suka yi da'awar wariyar launin fata kuma an yi niyyar  karkatar da hankali daga rashin ikon gwamnatinsa na dakile cutar .
Jaridar Daily Beast ta samu wata sakon waya daga gwamnatin Amurka da ke bayyana wani shiri na sadarwa da ake ganin ya fito ne daga majalisar tsaron kasa, wanda dabarar da aka ambata ita ce:
An nemi mu yi ƙoƙari mu isar da wannan saƙo ta kowane hanya da za mu iya, musamman a taron manema labarai da kuma a talabijin. Ƙungiyoyin labarai kamar su Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun yi iƙirarin cewa ƙoƙarin da China ke yi na aika taimako ga ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa wani ɓangare ne na yaɗa labarai don samun rinjaye a duniya.
Shugaban EU Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai wani bangare na siyasa wanda ya shafi gwagwarmayar samun tasiri ta hanyar maganganu da kuma 'siyasa ta karimci'.
Borrell ya kuma ce  China tana dagewa kan cewa, sabanin Amurka, ita abokiyar aiki ce mai dogaro da abin dogaro .
China ta kuma yi kira ga Amurka da ta ɗage takunkumin da ta kakaba wa Syria, Venezuela da Iran, yayin da take aika taimako ga waɗannan ƙasashe biyu.
An dakatar da takunkumin Amurka kan takunkumin da Jack Ma ya bayar na takunkumin rufe fuska 100,000 da aka ba Cuba a ranar 3 ga watan Afrilu.
An kuma zargi hukumomin Amurka da karkatar da tallafi ga wasu ƙasashe zuwa ƙasarsu.
Kuma an kuma samu rahotanni game da wasu rikice-rikice da suka shafi abin rufe fuska tsakanin wasu ƙasashe, kamar Jamus, Austria da Switzerland, da Jamhuriyar Czech da Italiya.
Bugu da ƙari, Turkiyya ta kwace ɗaruruwan na'urorin numfashi da aka tura Spain.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta soki rashin haɗin kai na Tarayyar Turai ga Italiya, wadda cutar korona ta shafa.
Maurizio Massari, jakadan Italiya a EU, ya ce China ce kawai ta mayar da martani ta bangarorin biyu.
Wannan ba kyakkyawan alama ba ne ga haɗin kan Turai .
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, bayan ya yi magana da Firaministan Italiya Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya shirya sojojin Rasha don aika likitocin soja, motocin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman da sauran kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
Jaridar La Stampa ta Italiya ta kawo wani  babban majiyar siyasa  wanda ba a bayyana sunansa ba wanda ya ce kashi 80 cikin dari na taimakon Rasha  kadan ne ko kuma ba shi da amfani ga Italiya .
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da shiga wani mummunan aiki na siyasa da diflomasiyya.
Shugaban Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, da Ministan Harkokin Wajen Italiya Luigi Di Maio sun musanta rahoton da aka yi a kafofin yada labarai kuma sun nuna godiyarsu.
Rasha ta kuma aika da jirgin sama mai jigilar kayayyaki da kayan aikin likita zuwa Amurka.
Kakakin Kremlin Dmitry Peskov ya ce  a cikin bayar da taimakonsa ga abokan aikinsa na Amurka, [Putin] yana zaton cewa idan masana'antun Amurka na kayan aiki da kayan aikin likita suka sami saurin aiki, za su iya mayar da su idan an buƙata .
Za a rage girman atisayen sojin NATO na Defender 2020 da aka shirya yi a Jamus, Poland da Baltic, wanda shi ne mafi girma daga NATO tun bayan ƙarshen Cold War.
Babban sakataren Kamfen na Yaki da Makaman Nukiliya Kate Hudson ta soki atisayen Defender 2020:  A cikin matsalar lafiyar jama'a da ake ciki yanzu, ba wai kawai sojojin Amurka da kasashen Turai da ke halartar taron ba ne ke cikin haɗari, har ma da mutanen da ke cikin ƙasashen da suke aiki . Gwamnatin Iran ta yi fama da cutar sosai, tare da kusan 'yan majalisa 20 da suka kamu da cutar, da kuma wasu manyan jami'an siyasa 15 da ke aiki a yanzu da kuma waɗanda suka gabata.
Shugaban Iran Hassan Rouhani ya rubuta wata wasika a bude ga shugabannin duniya don neman taimako a ranar 14 ga Maris, 2020, yana mai cewa kasarsa na gwagwarmaya don magance cutar saboda rashin samun damar shiga kasuwannin duniya saboda takunkumin Amurka kan Iran. Cutar ta haifar da kira ga Amurka da ta aiwatar da manufofin zamantakewar da aka saba da sauran ƙasashe masu arziki, gami da tsarin kula da lafiya na duniya, shirin kula da yara na duniya, izinin iyaye da aka biya, da kuma ƙarin matakan tallafawa lafiyar jama'a.
Masu nazarin siyasa suna tsammanin hakan zai shafi damar da Donald Trump zai samu na sake zaɓe a zaɓen shugaban ƙasa na 2020. Dangantaka ta diflomasiyya tsakanin Japan da Koriya ta Kudu ta lalace saboda annobar.
