Bincike da yawa ya nuna cewa tawul ɗin takarda sun fi na lantarki tsabta da ake samu a bayan gida.
A shekara ta 2008, wani bincike da masana'antar takarda ta yi, wato European Tissue Symposium, ya yi da Jami'ar Westminster da ke Landan, don kwatanta tsabtace jiki da takarda takarda, busar hannu da iska da kuma busar hannu da iska.
