L-angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda ke da alaƙa da gefen waje (ƙwayoyin sel) na ƙwayoyin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
LACE2 yana hana aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin dangiotensin II da kuma kara lAng (1-7) wanda ya sa ya zama kyakkyawan makamin magani don magance cututtukan zuciya. LACE2 kuma shine wurin shiga cikin ƙwayoyin wasu coronavirus.
Ana kiran kwayar halitta ta ɗan adam hACE2.
Angiotensin Converting Enzyme 2 wani sinadarin zinc ne wanda yake kan farfajiyar ƙwayoyin endothelial da sauran ƙwayoyin.
Protein ACE2 yana dauke da yankin peptidase M2 mai ƙare N da yankin renal amino acid transporter collectrin mai ƙare C.
LACE2 shine nau'in furotin mai wucewa guda ɗaya na nau'in I, wanda yankin aikin enzymatic ya bayyana akan farfajiyar ƙwayoyin huhu da sauran kyallen takarda.
Wani sinadarin da ake kira sheddase ne yake raba sashen waje na ACE2 daga sashen da ke cikin ƙwayoyin cuta, kuma sai ya fitar da furotin da ke cikin jini kuma ya fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
LACE2 yana cikin yawancin gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin salula na ƙwayoyin cuta na nau'in II na alveoli, ƙananan ƙwayoyin hanji, ƙwayoyin jini da ƙwayoyin jini da ƙwayoyin jini na ƙwayoyin tsoka a yawancin gabobin jiki.
Ana kuma nuna mRNA na ACE2 a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Aikin farko na ACE2 shi ne ya daidaita ACE.
Ƙwayoyin cuta suna raba ƙwayar angiotensin I zuwa ƙwayar angiotensin II.
ACE2 kuma yana raba amino acid phenylamine mai ƙare carboxyl na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana haɓaka shi zuwa angiotensin mai fadada jini (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
LACE2 na iya rarraba wasu peptides da yawa ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, lapelin, neurotensin, dynorphine A, da ghrelin.
LACE2 kuma yana sarrafa yaduwar membrane na mai jigilar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma yana da hannu cikin cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ACE2 shine babban wurin shiga cikin ƙwayoyin wasu coronavirus, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaurewar furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa yankin enzymatic na ACE2 a saman sel yana haifar da endocytosis da kuma sauyawar kwayar cutar da enzyme a cikin endosomes a cikin sel.
