Allurar rigakafin COVID-19 allurar rigakafi ce da ake tsammani da za ta iya hana cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19).
Ko da yake babu wani allurar da ta wuce gwajin asibiti, ana ƙoƙarin yin wasu gwaje-gwaje.
A ƙarshen watan Fabrairun 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ce ba a sa ran samun allurar rigakafin cutar SARS-CoV-2 ba, cutar da ke haifar da cutar, har zuwa aƙalla watanni 18.
A watan Afrilu, an yi gwajin lafiya na farko kan alluran rigakafi biyar.
An gano COVID-19 a watan Disamba na 2019.
Wani babban annobar cuta ya ɓarke a duniya a shekarar 2020, wanda ya haifar da saka hannun jari da bincike mai yawa don samar da allurar rigakafi.
Ƙungiyoyi da yawa suna amfani da ƙwayoyin halittar da aka buga don haɓaka alluran rigakafin SARS-CoV-2.
An bayyana a watan Afrilu, abubuwan da ke buƙatar CEPI don samar da allurar rigakafi sune sauri, iya samarwa, turawa da samun dama a duniya.
A watan Afrilu, masana kimiyya na CEPI sun ba da rahoton cewa kamfanonin fasaha daban-daban 10 suna gudanar da bincike da ayyukan ci gaba a farkon 2020 da nufin samar da allurar rigakafin COVID-19.
Manufofin babban dandamali wanda aka ƙaddamar da shi a cikin binciken I na Tsaro sun haɗa da:
nucleic acid (DNA da RNA) (lokaci na farko mai haɓaka da mai neman allurar rigakafi: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
mai ɗaukar hoto (lokaci na farko mai haɓaka da mai neman rigakafi: CanSino Biologics, mai ɗaukar hoto na adenoviral na 5)
Kamar yadda masana kimiyya na CEPI suka bayyana a watan Afrilu, jimillar alluran rigakafi 115 suna cikin matakan farko na ci gaba, 78 (79 bisa ga Cibiyar Milken) an tabbatar da aiki da kuma wasu 37 da aka sanar, amma tare da ɗan bayani na jama'a (wanda ake tsammanin a cikin shiri ko zane).
Gwajin Mataki na I-II yana gudanar da gwajin farko na aminci da rigakafi, yawanci ana sarrafa shi ta hanyar bazuwar, ana sarrafa shi da wuribo kuma ana gudanar dashi a wurare da yawa, yana ƙayyade ƙarin ƙayyadaddun allurai masu tasiri.
Gwaje-gwaje na Mataki na III yawanci sun haɗa da mahalarta da yawa, gami da ƙungiyar sarrafawa, kuma suna gwada ingancin allurar rigakafin don hana cutar, yayin lura da tasirin sakamako mara kyau a mafi kyawun sashi.
Daga cikin alluran rigakafi 79 da ake ci gaba da su (wanda aka tabbatar a farkon Afrilu 2020), 74 ba su riga sun fara gwaji a kan mutane ba (har yanzu a cikin bincike  kafin asibiti ).
